      "rendered": "5 Mobile Fundraising Apps for Do-Gooders and Nonprofits"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/5-Mobile-Fundraising-App-for-Nonprofits.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-14880\" alt=\"5 Mobile Fundraising App for Nonprofits\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/5-Mobile-Fundraising-App-for-Nonprofits-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/5-Mobile-Fundraising-App-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/5-Mobile-Fundraising-App-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/5-Mobile-Fundraising-App-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/5-Mobile-Fundraising-App-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/5-Mobile-Fundraising-App-for-Nonprofits.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Since the launch of the iPhone on June 29, 2007 many mobile fundraising apps have been released, but few have been successful. Some apps were based on good ideas, but ahead of their time and others simply weren&#8217;t good enough to keep users interested. Six years later the design and functionality of fundraising apps has improved significantly.\u00a0Still in their infancy, it&#8217;s assured that mobile apps will play a dominant fundraising role in the future and nonprofits would be wise to download and study the next generation of fundraising apps listed below.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. I Can Go Without<br />\n<a href=\"http://icangowithout.com/\">icangowithout.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/i-can-go-without-charity-micro/id669261809\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14861\" alt=\"download nonprofit fundraising iphone app\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundraising-iphone-app.png?resize=152%2C51\" width=\"152\" height=\"51\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundraising-iphone-app.png?w=152&amp;ssl=1 152w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundraising-iphone-app.png?resize=150%2C51&amp;ssl=1 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 152px) 100vw, 152px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">An app that encourages users to pledge to make lifestyle changes (such as giving up a cup a coffee each week) and then enables users to donate the money not spent to nonprofits.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://icangowithout.com/#top\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14855\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"i can go without app\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/i-can-go-without-app.png?resize=600%2C359\" width=\"600\" height=\"359\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/i-can-go-without-app.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/i-can-go-without-app.png?resize=300%2C179&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. HelpBridge<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/about/corporatecitizenship/en-us/nonprofits/helpbridge.aspx\">microsoft.com/helpbridge</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">An app that enables users to donate via text, send messages to emergency contacts, and browse volunteer opportunities during crisis situations.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/store/app/helpbridge/f57af950-e37e-403b-b71d-b8856fab2b15\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14873\" alt=\"Windows Phone 159\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Windows-Phone-159.jpg?resize=159%2C50\" width=\"159\" height=\"50\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/helpbridge/id576543879\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14861\" alt=\"download nonprofit fundraising iphone app\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundraising-iphone-app.png?resize=152%2C51\" width=\"152\" height=\"51\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundraising-iphone-app.png?w=152&amp;ssl=1 152w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundraising-iphone-app.png?resize=150%2C51&amp;ssl=1 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 152px) 100vw, 152px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.microsoft.helpbridge&amp;feature=search_result#?t=W251bGwsMSwyLDEsImNvbS5taWNyb3NvZnQuaGVscGJyaWRnZSJd\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14862\" alt=\"download nonprofit fundaising android app\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundaising-android-app.png?resize=152%2C51\" width=\"152\" height=\"51\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundaising-android-app.png?w=152&amp;ssl=1 152w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundaising-android-app.png?resize=150%2C51&amp;ssl=1 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 152px) 100vw, 152px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/about/corporatecitizenship/en-us/nonprofits/helpbridge.aspx\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14872\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"HelpBridge\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/HelpBridge.png?resize=600%2C381\" width=\"600\" height=\"381\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/HelpBridge.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/HelpBridge.png?resize=300%2C190&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Google One Today<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.google.com/onetoday/\">google.com/onetoday</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.apps.onetoday\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14862\" alt=\"download nonprofit fundaising android app\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundaising-android-app.png?resize=152%2C51\" width=\"152\" height=\"51\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundaising-android-app.png?w=152&amp;ssl=1 152w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundaising-android-app.png?resize=150%2C51&amp;ssl=1 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 152px) 100vw, 152px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">An app that enables users to donate $1 a day to their favorite nonprofits.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.google.com/onetoday/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14857\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Google One Today\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Google-One-Today.png?resize=600%2C352\" width=\"600\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Google-One-Today.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Google-One-Today.png?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Check-in for Good<br />\n<a href=\"http://checkinforgood.com/\">checkinforgood.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">An app that enables users to check-in to participating retail locations to generate micro-donations to nonprofits.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/check-in-for-good/id536219052?mt=8\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14861\" alt=\"download nonprofit fundraising iphone app\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundraising-iphone-app.png?resize=152%2C51\" width=\"152\" height=\"51\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundraising-iphone-app.png?w=152&amp;ssl=1 152w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundraising-iphone-app.png?resize=150%2C51&amp;ssl=1 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 152px) 100vw, 152px\" /></a><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=checkinforgood.com\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14862\" alt=\"download nonprofit fundaising android app\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundaising-android-app.png?resize=152%2C51\" width=\"152\" height=\"51\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundaising-android-app.png?w=152&amp;ssl=1 152w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundaising-android-app.png?resize=150%2C51&amp;ssl=1 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 152px) 100vw, 152px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://checkinforgood.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14868\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"checkin for good\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/checkin-for-good.png?resize=600%2C300\" width=\"600\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/checkin-for-good.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/checkin-for-good.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Charity Miles<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.charitymiles.org/\">charitymiles.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">An app that enables users to earn money for charity when they walk, run, or bike.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/charity-miles/id505253234?mt=8\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14861\" alt=\"download nonprofit fundraising iphone app\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundraising-iphone-app.png?resize=152%2C51\" width=\"152\" height=\"51\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundraising-iphone-app.png?w=152&amp;ssl=1 152w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundraising-iphone-app.png?resize=150%2C51&amp;ssl=1 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 152px) 100vw, 152px\" /></a><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.charitymilescm.android\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14862\" alt=\"download nonprofit fundaising android app\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundaising-android-app.png?resize=152%2C51\" width=\"152\" height=\"51\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundaising-android-app.png?w=152&amp;ssl=1 152w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/download-nonprofit-fundaising-android-app.png?resize=150%2C51&amp;ssl=1 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 152px) 100vw, 152px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.charitymiles.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14870\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"charity miles\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/charity-miles.png?resize=600%2C369\" width=\"600\" height=\"369\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/charity-miles.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/charity-miles.png?resize=300%2C184&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n",
